  • Simple and cute, ready for you

    A simple yet cute addition to your wardrobe! Featuring a cute white bear waving on the front making it a must-have for any bear lover. Whether you're hanging out with friends or just relaxing, this tee promises both comfort and style.

    Available in 8 colors and 8 different sizes     for all to wear, measurements are shown below. It is best to measure your chest and length, and then choose a size according to the result to simplify the various international measurements.

     Max temperature 30c, or cold water. Reverse the garment to protect the print.

     Do not bleach

     Dry by the sun or hang it to dry.
